{"tid":1336330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【撐警集會】疑團體銀彈請人撐場 黑衣女持名單金鐘站外派錢予多人","createTime":"2019-07-21T02:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T08:13:37.000Z","uid":74778,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"caa7e8d766552d1bd5d9e050ce22e3d636627157","tid":1336330,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【撐警集會】疑團體銀彈請人撐場 黑衣女持名單金鐘站外派錢予多人</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n建制派今日傍晚5至7時舉行撐警集會，大會聲稱有31.6萬人參與，警方則指高峰期有10.3萬人。有讀者則向《蘋果》提供一段短片，指傍晚時分目擊有人在港鐵金鐘站附近進行錢銀交易，質疑團體派錢請人去集會。<br />\n<br />\n讀者Andy今日傍晚約6時於金鐘港鐵站C出口發現有一名黑衣女子向圍着她的人派錢。從片段可見，黑衣眼鏡女子手持一張名單及一疊一百元面值等的紙幣，被一男四女包圍，眾人有說有笑，片段中有人說「英姐」、「佢話去你度攞吖嘛」、「佢話畀9個咪畀9個你囉」，中段一名綠衣婦人左手拿住一疊500元，右手把2張100元遞給黑衣女子，問「係咪要簽收？」女子回應「係」，後來老婦便把500元放到自己袋裏。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190721/59845436?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190721%2F59845436%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82W8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=35926ea3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190721%2F59845436%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e356d337\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190721/59845436?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其實個政府做緊乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n同KOL買like有無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d26dafc5034527d4e274355cf198780fc70ee060","tid":1336330,"uid":77092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fef65416a7322ee5bc4a699b2e5ce6148e88d1c","tid":1336330,"uid":259530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42049761cbb2e107974e9ef74b1b9b7f2dddfa77","tid":1336330,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5d7743a648ce0fc4c69055aeaba459301b2b9d","tid":1336330,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:34:28.000Z","msg":"算啦人所共知既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6cb5474fe3dd4fe4264b12fc678730bffb9c15","tid":1336330,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1XgrGt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1XgrGt.jpg&h=a79dfcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnzVHeO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnzVHeO.png&h=d4bc950e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2a970239069a79b578c0f31a93a439333b4d558","tid":1336330,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"好心用支付寶過數la"},{"pid":"67e0b001ec79eb8c8b431df04b6f417b5c7fca42","tid":1336330,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"俾錢集會<br />\n中資威迫員工遊行<br />\n攪咁多野先得幾萬人出席<br />\n係咪維穩費唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe32b984b69902e0a31159682470773e0933e853","tid":1336330,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"<im